sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AuthMiddleware
    participant PermissionMiddleware
    participant FastAPI
    participant PostgreSQL
    
    Client->>AuthMiddleware: Request with JWT
    AuthMiddleware->>AuthMiddleware: Validate JWT token
    AuthMiddleware->>PermissionMiddleware: Check RBAC permissions
    PermissionMiddleware->>PostgreSQL: Verify user roles
    PermissionMiddleware->>FastAPI: Allow/deny access
    FastAPI->>Client: Response or 403 Forbidden